      "recording_attendee_id": "b0b88152-9448-4da3-8c7d-b6e8cf64c9a2",
      "order_number": 3,
      "text": "Yeah. Um wanted to reach out um I work with a.com, we are an Internet listing service. I saw that you guys are uh leasing right now for fall of two thousand and twenty-one And we work with some other properties in the area, with we have an exclusive partnership with facebook marketplace, facebook rental ads, things of that nature. And just wanted to see how you guys are going about filling those um openings and if there might be an opportunity, obviously not today, I know the end of the day is um coming close, but I wanted to check and see if we could set something up maybe later this week uh to go over"
